Getting Started ROS (Robotic Operating Systems)

by Aldi Farhan Fahrosa
Instrumentation, Brawijaya University

Instalasi Robot 
Link Rujukan --> https://github.com/UniversalRobots/Universal_Robots_ROS_Driver

1. Install ROS pada device yang digunakan, untuk ubuntu 20.04 gunakan ROS Noetic
   Link Rujukan http://wiki.ros.org/noetic/Installation/Ubuntu
2. Setup your sources.list
   >> sudo sh -c 'echo "deb http://packages.ros.org/ros/ubuntu $(lsb_release -sc) main" > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ros-latest.list'
3. Set up your keys
   >> sudo apt install curl # if you haven't already installed curl
   >> curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ros/rosdistro/master/ros.asc | sudo apt-key add -
4. Installation
   >> sudo apt update
   >> sudo apt install ros-noetic-desktop-full
5. Environment Setup
   >> source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash
   >> echo "source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash" >> ~/.bashrc
      source ~/.bashrc
6. Dependencies for building packages
   >> sudo apt install python3-rosdep python3-rosinstall python3-rosinstall-generator python3-wstool build-essential
   
   Initialize Rosdep
   >> sudo apt install python3-rosdep
   >> sudo rosdep init
   >> rosdep update

7. Instalasi Driver ( Link Rujukan -> https://github.com/ros-industrial/universal_robot)
   >> sudo apt-get install ros-noetic-universal-robots

Building From Source

1. Buat Catkin Workspace (Link Rujukan --> https://wiki.ros.org/catkin/Tutorials/create_a_workspace)
   >> source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash
   >> mkdir -p ~/catkin_ws/src
   >> cd ~/catkin_ws/
   >> catkin_make
   >> source devel/setup.bash
2. Build from sources in a Catkin workspace 
   >> cd $HOME/catkin_ws/src
   >> git clone -b noetic-devel https://github.com/ros-industrial/universal_robot.git
   >> cd $HOME/catkin_ws
   >> rosdep update
   >> rosdep install --rosdistro $ROS_DISTRO --ignore-src --from-paths src
   >> catkin_make #building
   >> source $HOME/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash # Activate Workspace
3. Gazebo Simulation 
   - Buka Terminal 1 
     >> roscore (Opsional, langsung ke Terminal 2, Pastikan running di catkin_ws dengan cd ~/catkin_ws && catkin_make)
   - Buka Terminal 2
     >> roslaunch ur_gazebo ur3_bringup.launch
   - Buka Terminal 3
     >> roslaunch ur3_moveit_config moveit_planning_execution.launch sim:=true
   - Buka Terminal 4 
     >> roslaunch ur3_moveit_config moveit_rviz.launch

4. Install Commander Moveit (untuk menjalankan UR dengan Python)
   >> sudo apt-get install ros-noetic-moveit
   >> rosrun ur3_moveit ur3_move.py
     
5. Real Universal Robot UR3CB
   >> roslaunch ur_calibration calibration_correction.launch robot_ip:=192.168.1.107 target_filename:="$(rospack find ur_calibration)/etc/ex-ur3_calibration.yaml"

   >> roslaunch ur_robot_driver ur3_bringup.launch robot_ip:=192.168.1.107 [reverse_port:=REVERSE_PORT] kinematics_config:=$(rospack find ur_calibration)/etc/ex-ur3_calibration.yaml

   >> roslaunch ur3_moveit_config moveit_planning_execution.launch limited:=true

   >> roslaunch ur3_moveit_config moveit_rviz.launch config:=true


source kinematics/bin/activate
   
